sentence: what are the cities of the state with the lowest point ?
sentence-with-vars: what are the cities of the state with the lowest point ?
sql: select city.city_name from city , highlow where city.state_name = highlow.state_name and highlow.lowest_elevation = ( select min ( highlow.lowest_elevation ) from highlow ) ;
